game.name: Moana Foot Surgery
game.description:
Moana is not an exotic princess of an island anymore. She left that place several years ago and moved to a city and started studying in a college. This modern day princess loves walking on each morning. But, today is not her day as she got injured while going to walk near to her home. Her ankle is broken and now she needs the medical treatment urgently. Are you ready to play the role of her doctor? Join Moana Foot Surgery game and be prepared to provide him with the instant ankle surgery!

The pain in her foot seems to be unbearable and her problem becomes worse if she does not obtain the treatment on time. Being her private physician, you have examined her foot and decided to give her the instant surgery. Make sure to provide your girl with the needful courage and to do everything that could keep her relax. After giving her the needful treatment, remember to allow her enjoy a perfect manicure which she likes the most. 

Apply the foot cream and then come to polish her nails to provide her with a relaxing foot spa in this one of the best foot care games for girls! Mix and match all colors and multiple patterns to prepare a combination of awesome nail polish! Begin your nail art design with the help of new nail polish! Make sure to add lovely matching ornaments to complete her nails in this html5 nail polish game. Complete your task by selecting a wonderful anklet for the lady in this princess makeover game! Enjoy more surgery games for kids online, no download required!
